jasima.shopSim.util
Class TextFileReader

java.lang.Object
  jasima.shopSim.util.TextFileReader

public class TextFileReader
extends Object

This class configures a StaticShopModel based on the contents of a text file. This class is used mostly for test purposes. For examples of the file structure see the examples in the directory "testInstances".

Author:
Torsten Hildebrandt
